---
---

<section class="pricing section-pad">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label section-label-light pricing-reveal">La inversión</p>
    <h2 class="pricing-h2 pricing-reveal">Precio visible<br />antes de la llamada.</h2>

    <div class="pricing-cards pricing-reveal">
      <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--main">
        <p class="pricing-card-eyebrow">Fee mensual</p>
        <p class="pricing-amount">$1.000.000<span class="pricing-sep">–</span>$1.200.000</p>
        <p class="pricing-period">CLP / mes · cobrado por adelantado</p>
        <p class="pricing-card-note">
          Cubre el sistema completo: Search Ads, landing, tracking, WhatsApp y SEO local. La pauta va siempre aparte.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--setup">
        <p class="pricing-card-eyebrow">Setup inicial</p>
        <p class="pricing-amount">$400.000<span class="pricing-sep">–</span>$700.000</p>
        <p class="pricing-period">CLP · único · no reembolsable</p>
        <p class="pricing-card-note">
          Cubre instrumentación, landing, tracking y aprendizaje inicial. Sin setup, el tiempo de entrega lo financia la
          agencia. No es el modelo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--media">
        <p class="pricing-card-eyebrow">Pauta publicitaria</p>
        <p class="pricing-amount pricing-amount--alt">Aparte</p>
        <p class="pricing-period">pagada por el cliente directamente a Google</p>
        <p class="pricing-card-note">
          El cliente es propietario de sus cuentas publicitarias. La pauta no pasa por la agencia. Sin opacidad,
          sin markup.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-roi pricing-reveal">
      <p class="pricing-roi-eyebrow">La matemática</p>
      <p class="pricing-roi-text">
        Un implante cerrado en Santiago deja entre <strong>$800.000 y $1.200.000</strong>. Dos cierres al mes cubren
        el fee. Si agregas un caso de ortodoncia, el retorno ya es obvio. El trabajo es instalar el sistema para que
        eso sea medible y repetible.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing {
    background: var(--color-forest);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .pricing-h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-h2-size);
    font-weight: var(--text-h2-weight);
    letter-spacing: var(--text-h2-track);
    line-height: var(--text-h2-leading);
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-block: 0 4rem;
  }

  .pricing-cards {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pricing-cards {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .pricing-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.625rem;
  }

  .pricing-card--main {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .pricing-card-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .pricing-amount {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.8vw, 32px);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .pricing-amount--alt {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .pricing-sep {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    margin-inline: 0.2em;
  }

  .pricing-period {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pricing-card-note {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    padding-top: 1rem;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .pricing-roi {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-orange);
    padding-left: 1.75rem;
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  .pricing-roi-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .pricing-roi-text {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.8vw, 18px);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }

  .pricing-roi-text strong {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
